title: _STORAGE_OFFLOAD_READ_OUTPUT (ntddstor.h)
description: The STORAGE_OFFLOAD_READ_OUTPUT structure is the output of an IOCTL_STORAGE_MANAGE_DATA_SET_ATTRIBUTES control code request when the Action member of DEVICE_DSM_INPUT is set to DeviceDsmAction_OffloadRead.
